PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 2001-2194 of November 27, 2001 respecting the appointment of SUSAN LeBLANC ROBICHAUD as director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission by adding the words "in the place of Susan Bartlett-Nelson, whose term will expire".

precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 2001-2194 of November 27, 2001
respecting the appointment of SUSAN LeBLANC ROBICHAUD as director of the
Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission by adding the words
"in the place of Susan Bartlett-Nelson, whose term will expire".
